{"title":"STM32F103RCT6核心板设计","uid":"7742e69e813648d5c85a45d015f995f0","slug":"STM32F103RCT6核心板设计","date":"2023-10-20T13:50:03.000Z","updated":"2023-11-05T15:21:35.606Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/STM32F103RCT6核心板设计.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/20/NiqwxTIlbRLvh1H.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"原理图\"><a href=\"#原理图\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原理图\"></a>原理图</h1><h2 id=\"总览\"><a href=\"#总览\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总览\"></a>总览</h2><p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/29/q64KdtoCr8uDjRz.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-10-29 174452.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"功能\"><a href=\"#功能\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"功能\"></a>功能</h2><p>1.四按键模块（共阴极）<br>2.ST-LINK接口<br>3.TypeC通信和XH座子通信<br>4.内置CH340可以串口ISP<br>5.外部FLASH和EEPROM<br>6.2个引脚LED<br>7.7线0.96寸OLED屏接口<br>8.拉出STM32F103RCT6基本所有引脚<br>9.蜂鸣器<br>10.可使用跳线和按键控制外部设备的启动</p>\n<p>应该加个电源开关的，搞忘了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"电源模块\"><a href=\"#电源模块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"电源模块\"></a>电源模块</h3><p>采用AMS1117-3.3线性稳压器<br>性能一般般，主要是便宜，设计的电路也不复杂，相比其他什么开关电源（MP2315之类的），发热比较严重吧，纹波也比较大。</p>\n<h3 id=\"蜂鸣器\"><a href=\"#蜂鸣器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"蜂鸣器\"></a>蜂鸣器</h3><p>可使用有源蜂鸣器or无源蜂鸣器</p>\n<h3 id=\"\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"\"></a></h3><h1 id=\"PCB设计\"><a href=\"#PCB设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"PCB设计\"></a>PCB设计</h1><p>使用四层板<br>toplayer:信号层1<br>innerlayer1:5V内电层<br>innerlayer2:3V3内电层<br>bottomlayer:信号层2</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/29/QwF3tHmRk8AbqYi.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-10-29 174830.png\"><br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/29/uPgDT42UnvWB8RQ.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-10-29 174820.png\"><br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/29/r5PASdp12CfRXwK.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-10-29 174910.png\"><br><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/29/8jqgEpcCWwKhezi.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-10-29 174921.png\"></p>\n<p>:::tip</p>\n<ol>\n<li>在设计晶振时需要保证晶振电路和其他电路相隔离（通过GND），保证晶振的高频信号不会对其他电路产生电磁干扰。</li>\n<li>芯片的电源输入一定要有旁路电容接地（经验值100nF），而且该电容一定要放在芯片电源引脚边上，保证信号的回路尽量短，该电容其实很有讲究的，功能挺多的，感兴趣之后可以再讨论。</li>\n<li>高频信号尽量不过两次孔，低频信号不过三次孔，减少过孔寄生效应的不利影响，高频信号线之间尽量铺GND隔离，需要严格同步时序的高频信号要保证信号线长度相等。</li>\n<li>焊接时候先焊电源，不然电源一炸之后的单片机也跟着炸，直接输光光。<br>:::</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"物理尺寸\"><a href=\"#物理尺寸\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"物理尺寸\"></a>物理尺寸</h1><p>整板大小：7cm x 6cm<br>定位孔：M3<br>OLED定位孔：M2</p>\n<h1 id=\"后记\"><a href=\"#后记\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"后记\"></a>后记</h1><p>本板子还未经验证，等验证完之后我会开源在JLC。<br>之后还会设计一个扩展板用于心电检测。</p>\n<p>PS: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>本来想着把板子做小，做成6*6，奈何layout水平不够。。。</li>\n<li>在最后布地线是真的折磨，我本来以为最后铺铜就可以保证大部分GND相连了。。最后还是改了半个多小时。。。（还好这个板子可以全部设备共地，不用分什么模拟地、数字地、直流地、交流地的）</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"参考资料\"><a href=\"#参考资料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考资料\"></a>参考资料</h1><h2 id=\"数据手册\"><a href=\"#数据手册\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据手册\"></a>数据手册</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.alldatasheet.com/datasheet-pdf/pdf/1132602/WCH/CH340.html\">CH340</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://datasheet.lcsc.com/lcsc/2001181032_BOYAMICRO-BY25Q64ASSIG-T_C484306.pdf\">BY25Q64ASSIG</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.alldatasheet.com/datasheet-pdf/pdf/56063/ATMEL/AT24C02.html\">AT24C02</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.alldatasheet.com/datasheet-pdf/pdf/49118/ADMOS/AMS1117.html\">ASM1117</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.st.com/resource/en/datasheet/stm32f103rc.pdf\">STM32F1x</a></li>\n</ol></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"PCB布线原则\"><a href=\"#PCB布线原则\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"PCB布线原则\"></a>PCB布线原则</h2><p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zerokingwang/article/details/127651767\">https://blog.csdn.net/zerokingwang/article/details/127651767</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"STM32F103RCT6学习开发用...","permalink":"/post/STM32F103RCT6核心板设计","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":948,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Electronic","slug":"Electronic","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Electronic.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"STM32","slug":"STM32","count":2,"path":"api/tags/STM32.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E5%9B%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">原理图</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E8%A7%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总览</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text